      "text": "Dividend is more of a hurdle clearing step - needs to cross the hurdle of a dividend paying bank. if you could give less than 25 paise, vedi would have done that. The bank has consistently faced curve balls - and these are not from outside, but a result of internal weakness - who asked them to go whole hog on MFI, no other universal bank got their numbers dragged like IDFC. Then this fraud - who else can be hele responsible but the management itself.. the cost of all these fracas is borne by us poor shareholders who see their holding diluted at low levels. On the credit side is the admirable N…",
